Gitter:
You can check out general chat about Operating System u here: https://gitter.im/OperatingSystemU/Operating-System-U-Chat-General
This is for talk about OSu overall, each repo has it's own Gitter channel which is listed in the Gitter file of that repo.
This repo has no Gitter and the general chat should be used for talk about this repo.
Gitter will be used in this project to allow contributers and developers to easily be able to chat with each other and communicate.
Gitter can and hopefully will be used for collaborating more efficently and it is encouraged that contributer's utilize gitter.
